WCB Wasafi signee Zuchu is nursing a knee injury after being involved in an accident. Zuchu shared news of the accident with a video of her knee getting patched up after the road accident. "I was involved in a minor accident that left me with a knee Injury yesterday night, ahead of my scheduled show in Nigeria," she said. "Canceling a show is one of the hardest decisions, siwezi as an artiste, leo ndo nimejua. It is a hard decision as an artiste. I will go as I am, injuries and all." The 'Sukari' hitmaker went on to ask her fans to say a silent prayer for her. "My health is more important. And I would feel even worse if i cancelled on my fans. I will push myself and perform well on stage."